# ===============================================================
# .gitignore para projetos SQL Server | .gitignore for SQL Server projects
# Author: Rafael Binda
# ===============================================================

# --- Arquivos de sistema e IDE (SSMS / VS) | System and IDE files (SSMS / VS) ---
.vs/
**/.vs/
*.suo
*.user
*.userosscache
*.sln.docstates
*.slnx
VSWorkspaceState.json
.DS_Store

# --- Arquivos de Cache e Banco de Dados Local | Cache and Local Database files ---
*.sqlite
*.db
*.cache

# --- Arquivos Temporários | Temporary Files ---
*.tmp
*.temp
*.old
*.orig
*.log

# --- Arquivos de Banco de Dados (Dados Reais) | Database Files (Actual Data) ---
# Ignora arquivos de dados para evitar subir DBs pesados ao GitHub
*.mdf
*.ldf
*.ndf

# --- Backups e Logs de Transação | Backups and Transaction Logs ---
*.bak
*.trn

# --- Arquivos Temporários de Office | Office Temporary Files ---
~$*
*.tmp.docx
*.tmp.xlsx
*.tmp.pptx
*.tmp.pdf

# --- Exceções (Arquivos que DEVEM ser mantidos) | Exceptions (Files to KEEP) ---
!.sql
!.md
!LICENSE
!README.md
